# Feature modules

- No imports between sibling features.
- No direct `@radix-ui/*` or `@base-ui/*` — use `@/components/ui/*`.
- Public exports through `index.ts`.
- Section UI composes `shared/ui` + shadcn + content from `loadPortfolio()`.
